Jaya Narasimha Śrī Narasimha
Author: Vyāsadeva
ook Name: Brahmanda Purana
jaya narasimha śrī narasimha jaya jaya narasimhadeva
praladesa jaya padma mukha padma bhṛnga
TRANSLATION
Glories to Lord Nṛsimha, Śrī Nṛsimha, All Glories to Lord Nrsimhadeva. The Lord of Prahlada, like a honeybee, is always engaged in beholding the lotuslike face of the goddess of fortune.
